Name: Practice Book for Conceptual Physics Fundamentals

ReviewList.Text: this book really helps tie in a lot of the things you will learn in an intro to physics class... instead of just reading from text all the time this gives you a way to actually apply those concepts to real like situations
It was much cheaper than buying it in the bookstore, and served the same purpose. Loved to have it, and by the way got a average 99% (A+) for this course.
